  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prospective, comparative, randomized single surgeon study comparing minimally invasive
      total hip arthroplasty (MIS) via anterior approach to conventional total hip arthroplasty via
      anterolateral transgluteal approach.
    </textblock>
